Package: decotur
Type: Package
Title: DeCoTUR (Detecting Coevolving Traits Using Relatives)
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Rohan Mehta
Maintainer: Rohan Mehta <rsmeht4@emory.edu>
Description: This package provides functions to compute the coevolution score, a method to detect interactions betweeen binary traits (such as SNPs, or the presence/absence of accessory genes in a bacterial genome).
    Additional helper functions are also provided. Preprint: https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2022.03.14.484367v1
License: Open-source
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
        progress,
        ggplot2
Imports:
        igraph,
        stats,
        utils,
        pbapply,
        PoissonBinomial,
        ggplot2
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Suggests: 
    rmarkdown,
    knitr,
    ggplot2
VignetteBuilder: 
    knitr,
    ggplot2
